Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.67,0:00:05.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.35,0:00:13.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.59,0:00:33.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.31,0:00:36.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The sound resonates\NInto my heart, so hard and deep
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.29,0:00:40.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A field of stars spans endlessly\NAnd through it I carve a passageway
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.25,0:00:42.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In step with time as generations change
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.19,0:00:44.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Close your eyes and listen closely
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.22,0:00:47.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shooting stars stream on silently…\Nuntil the goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.29,0:00:50.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep the light inside of you,\Nnever give up don't ever lose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.29,0:00:52.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Transcend time and you will prove,\Nthere is a special place for you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.14,0:00:53.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A blaze of glory is there,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.93,0:00:55.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's all a part of our estate;\Nlife is our story to create
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.75,0:01:01.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.64,0:01:05.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes speak from ages old by voice of light\NThroughout the age, never fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.56,0:01:09.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A secret fire, a scream of light,\Nvoices calling through twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:11.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cast your thoughts to the wind,\Nhang your wishes on the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.39,0:01:13.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Live your life with all your strength\Nfor dreams will reach you very soon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.25,0:01:16.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.96,0:01:19.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes speak from ages old\Nby voice of light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.14,0:01:21.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Throughout the age,\Nnever fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.29,0:01:24.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Someday your dream will find\Nits place somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.68,0:01:28.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep shining like a star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.38,0:51:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.17,0:01:33.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Konpaku, Mod Souls…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.87,0:01:37.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,were fake souls created\Nto battle Hollows.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.46,0:01:42.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,However, the project was abandoned\Nas inhumane
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.29,0:01:46.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and the order was given\Nto destroy all of the Mod Souls, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.85,0:01:50.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Urahara Store
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.46,0:01:54.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.50,0:01:57.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Um…Mr. Kisuke…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.80,0:01:58.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.50,0:02:02.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Uh… I'm sorry…\NThis is all my fault…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.59,0:02:05.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're angry…\Naren't you…?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.29,0:02:11.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.29,0:02:17.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.\NWhy are you getting so scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.29,0:02:20.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're in this together, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.84,0:02:25.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I'll take care of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.80,0:02:27.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kisuke…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.29,0:02:33.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now…\NThere, there…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.34,0:02:36.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Manager, everything is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.29,0:02:41.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Shall we go to collect\Nour merchandise then?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.96,0:02:43.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Yes.\N– Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.65,0:02:53.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Uh…that guy…\NWhat's he doing all by himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.84,0:03:05.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I stay calm, I can easily\Nread your moves!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.09,0:03:14.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.92,0:03:16.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come back, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:17.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:19.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We have an order!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.05,0:03:22.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?! At a time like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:23.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A Hollow is about to appear!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.46,0:03:25.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's near!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.29,0:03:26.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.29,0:03:27.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.00,0:03:31.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.25,0:03:35.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hashigami! Kaneda! Ino…!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.34,0:03:38.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you yelling about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.59,0:03:40.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A strange high school student\Nattacked us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.34,0:03:43.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He had orange hair…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.63,0:03:44.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A high school student?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.75,0:03:46.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.96,0:03:48.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.84,0:03:50.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What can this be…?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:55.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I think you boys play\Ntoo many video games.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.96,0:03:58.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:04.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That Soul Reaper and those\Nkids ruined my good mood…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.36,0:04:04.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.75,0:04:06.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:09.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A Hollow…! I sense a Hollow…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.09,0:04:11.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's around where I was…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.46,0:04:16.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is it going to attack those kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.80,0:04:18.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kill him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.75,0:04:19.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hah-hah-hah…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.75,0:04:22.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So what? I'll make a better one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.46,0:04:28.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hah! "Clean up after school,"\Nshe says!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.46,0:04:32.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why should we do this?\NWhy doesn't she believe us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:35.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Probably because\Nwe're always misbehaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:37.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.21,0:04:40.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And she even confiscated our games.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.63,0:04:47.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.67,0:04:50.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My Soul Pager isn't working right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.13,0:04:50.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:52.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is the battery dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.29,0:04:53.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:55.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You should have bought some spare\Nbatteries instead of pining after a Chappie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:04:59.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't figure out the location\Nof the Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.30,0:05:00.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.88,0:05:11.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:16.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's that high school student!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:28.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.13,0:05:30.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Blood?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:42.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.59,0:05:44.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.55,0:05:45.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.71,0:05:48.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.75,0:05:49.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.29,0:05:51.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:53.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Hey, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.92,0:06:02.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You interfere with my meal,\Nthen you run all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.87,0:06:04.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:07.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but you're not strong enough to\Nbe messing with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.92,0:06:16.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.84,0:06:17.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:28.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You… Why…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.29,0:06:30.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,are you helping me –
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.29,0:06:32.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You! You're hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.96,0:06:35.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Whose body do you think this is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.80,0:06:39.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If a two-bit one like this\Ncan bloody you up this bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.05,0:06:40.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,don't even think about fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.05,0:06:41.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.71,0:06:45.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I had to fight it because\Nyou took so long getting here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.75,0:06:48.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! You're supposed to be\N a battle-ready Mod Soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.34,0:06:49.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How pitiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:50.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you two?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:53.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.55,0:07:07.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:26.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! How reckless\N can you be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:29.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Once you crack its head,\Nthe Hollow will disappear on its own!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.71,0:07:31.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And you had to...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.59,0:07:33.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– go kick it again.\N– There's no one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.34,0:07:35.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you boys pulling my leg?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.00,0:07:39.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No! It's true! You have to believe us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.17,0:07:43.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then, where is this bleeding\Nhigh school student?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.29,0:07:45.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But it's true… Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:49.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I want you to stay and\Nclean after school again tomorrow, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.50,0:07:54.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What…?! Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:55.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.59,0:08:02.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you hate them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.29,0:08:06.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So what? If I didn't help them,\Nthey would've been killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:09.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And I won't let anyone get killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.29,0:08:15.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Soon after I was created,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.05,0:08:19.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the Soul Society ordered\Nall Mod Souls be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.17,0:08:21.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.17,0:08:25.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,my date of death was determined\Nthe day after I was created.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.30,0:08:28.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.88,0:08:35.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I trembled in fear every day,\Ninside that pill,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.75,0:08:39.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,as I watched the others\Naround me disappear, day by day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.42,0:08:42.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I was able to slip out\Nof the warehouse
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.34,0:08:44.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,by hiding among other pills,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.63,0:08:48.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was always afraid that I would\Nsomeday be discovered and destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:52.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All the while, I wondered:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.00,0:08:56.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why should others determine my fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.09,0:09:02.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why can't I decide for myself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.17,0:09:06.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it up to me whether I live or die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.55,0:09:08.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's why…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.38,0:09:11.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I…won't kill anyone…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.25,0:09:15.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't want to see anyone killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.59,0:09:26.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my… Here I finally found you\Nand you're all battered up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.84,0:09:30.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like all the equipment\Nwe prepared was for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:31.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.42,0:09:40.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.29,0:09:49.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.96,0:09:51.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Collection completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.34,0:09:53.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.63,0:09:54.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.75,0:09:57.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I thought I'd finally\Nbe able to fight it out, after all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.67,0:09:59.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.17,0:09:59.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.92,0:10:01.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to\Ndo with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.55,0:10:02.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.84,0:10:05.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:10.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You can see me?\NWho are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.34,0:10:12.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, how can I answer that…?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.29,0:10:14.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A greedy merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.59,0:10:16.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you can't take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.96,0:10:18.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's this, Urahara?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.21,0:10:22.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you take back goods you've sold to\Npeople without giving them a refund?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.05,0:10:26.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, I guess I'll refund you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.92,0:10:30.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's not necessary.\NI'm satisfied with this item.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.55,0:10:34.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you guys work outside\Nthe laws of the Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.92,0:10:38.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're not really obligated\Nto collect these things, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.29,0:10:41.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't blame me if you run into trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.96,0:10:43.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to be hiding out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.29,0:10:47.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.\NI've gotten used to trouble lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.50,0:10:51.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.63,0:10:54.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.29,0:10:55.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, okay…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.13,0:11:15.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What's the matter, Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.29,0:11:19.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Man… Abusing my body,\Nknowing it wasn't his…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.13,0:11:23.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm talking to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.06,0:11:24.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.29,0:11:27.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You must look very\Nstrange to outsiders.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:31.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.29,0:11:34.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia, what do I do to\Ncomplain to him directly?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:38.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Well, you'd need to insert it\Ninto a body without a soul –
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.92,0:11:41.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,in other words, a dead body.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:43.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Got it! A dead body…!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.34,0:11:44.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see now…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.42,0:11:45.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to find one lying around!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.88,0:11:46.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Quit yapping.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.29,0:11:48.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.29,0:11:50.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.09,0:11:53.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.29,0:11:57.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,\Nall I need is a receptacle, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.29,0:12:00.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yes, but that's not…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.09,0:12:05.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but this body I'm in\Nisn't a real body either…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.13,0:12:06.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.97,0:12:10.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please pardon the inconvenience during\Nthe construction.\N		O-Okay, let's give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.71,0:12:13.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You sure? So, what do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:16.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You put it into its mouth, I guess…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:18.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay…like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.21,0:12:26.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Humph. It didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.13,0:12:28.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.05,0:12:31.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.09,0:12:35.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You! Ichigo Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.13,0:12:36.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I challenge you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.67,0:12:39.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, what…? Y-You're huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.59,0:12:41.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm small! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.63,0:12:44.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My hands have gotten so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.29,0:12:46.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ohh… I'm all soft!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.29,0:12:47.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you, Mod Soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.88,0:12:48.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.67,0:12:52.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think our discussion was over!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.29,0:12:52.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.88,0:12:56.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna take real good care of you!\NPrepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.96,0:12:59.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then I guess I'll take you on as I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.96,0:13:10.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wake up, Ichigo!\NIt's morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.21,0:13:11.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Morning! Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.29,0:13:13.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How's that? Give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:16.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you give up,\Nthen wake up and apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:19.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't, I'll get in your school bag\Nand follow you to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.30,0:13:20.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The girls in your class will say,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.59,0:13:24.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,"Oh, Kurosaki… you carry\Na stuffed animal around? How weird!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.17,0:13:28.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ow…! Let go of me, you…! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.29,0:13:33.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yammering away first thing\Nin the morning…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:36.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to shut up and\Nact like a stuffed animal, didn't I, Kon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.21,0:13:41.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why the heck are you calling me Kon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.80,0:13:44.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to call you Kaizo Konpaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:46.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kon's good enough for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,0:13:49.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's no reason for you\Nto call me Kon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.29,0:13:50.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it sound sort of silly?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.67,0:13:53.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I know! Why don't you\Ncall me Kai, instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.30,0:13:55.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I like Kai. Call me Kai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.29,0:13:56.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– No way.\N– Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.29,0:14:00.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Because Kai sounds kinda cool.\NI wouldn't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.00,0:14:02.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.09,0:14:04.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get smart! You…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.29,0:14:05.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's all this racket,\Nso early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.29,0:14:08.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even take\Nmy time changing clothes…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.55,0:14:09.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh…?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.75,0:14:11.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.30,0:14:17.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nice angle…\NI'm glad I'm a stuffed animal…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.34,0:14:20.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ow…! Stop it! Stop it!\NMy stuffing's coming out! My stuffing…!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:21.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.96,0:14:25.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kojima and Asano are…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.17,0:14:26.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.46,0:14:29.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.71,0:14:31.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,N-N-Nothing. I'm not doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.92,0:14:34.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing,\Nso early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.88,0:14:37.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't early anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.42,0:14:39.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kojima and Asano are waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.13,0:14:41.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.05,0:14:43.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! It's this late already?!\NOhhh! I'm going to be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:46.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your toast is ready,\Nso eat before you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.42,0:14:49.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I overslept!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.71,0:14:51.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right out, so wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.29,0:14:54.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this is unusual!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.71,0:14:56.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, take your time,\Nbut hurry, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.42,0:14:57.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.42,0:15:00.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Say…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:02.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.29,0:15:06.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You erased the memories of\Nmy classmates again, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.29,0:15:08.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.84,0:15:12.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't want them to remember\Nwhat happened yesterday, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.50,0:15:15.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well… I guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.59,0:15:18.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Too many things have\Nbeen happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.38,0:15:20.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and it's like…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:22.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,it's only natural…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.25,0:15:29.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, I'm going on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.80,0:15:32.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo…?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.21,0:15:33.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.29,0:15:34.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.59,0:15:37.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.59,0:15:42.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Tatsuki, your elective\Nwas art, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.50,0:15:43.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.25,0:15:46.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did you do your assignment,\N"Me in the Future"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:48.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I did. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.29,0:15:49.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's show each other\Nwhat we've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.75,0:15:51.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have no confidence at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.29,0:15:52.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.53,0:15:54.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.63,0:15:56.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you're good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.05,0:16:00.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be the female\Nvale tudo champion someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.25,0:16:02.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.29,0:16:04.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mine is too awful to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.09,0:16:07.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Orihime?\NWhat did you draw?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.38,0:16:09.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for asking!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:12.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, in my heart,\NI call it my masterpiece!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.15,0:16:14.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh really? Show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:16.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da…!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.71,0:16:19.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,"The Future Me"\N		Maximum speed: 380 kph!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.29,0:16:21.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,From my mouth,\Nflames of 20,000 degrees Celsius,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.29,0:16:23.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and from my eyes,\Nspecial destructive rays!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.76,0:16:25.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, Orihime! That's definitely not what\Nyou were supposed to draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:28.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Huh? What? Why…?\N– Do you want to get detention again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.09,0:16:30.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But wait, there's more…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.29,0:16:31.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:33.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.29,0:16:34.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.67,0:16:37.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good morning, Inoue!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.00,0:16:39.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.00,0:16:42.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's sure in a good mood today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.88,0:16:47.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he, Orihime?\NHuh? Orihime?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:49.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mmm… But…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:53.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru, what's the date today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.00,0:16:58.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's June 16…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.55,0:16:59.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:02.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's not in a good mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.33,0:17:07.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He acts like that when he's really tense.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:08.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:10.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuki…?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.80,0:17:13.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry…\NI know the reason why.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.50,0:17:19.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow,\Nhe's going to skip school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.29,0:17:24.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da! And now,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.86,0:17:28.33,On Top,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurasaki Clinic will be closed\Ntomorrow on the 17th.\N	I would like to\N	discuss our duties for tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.33,0:17:30.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And since, as your father,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.75,0:17:33.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I am the chairman,\NI get to make all of the decisions!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.00,0:17:37.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?\NYou can't call this a discussion!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.05,0:17:40.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Raise your hand if\Nyou want to speak, Chief of Staff!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.29,0:17:43.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,C-Chief of Staff…?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.63,0:17:45.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not exactly unhappy
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.80,0:17:48.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzu will be the lunch\Nstaff officer, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.46,0:17:49.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Aye aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:51.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Karin will be the porter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:53.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! What happened to\N"Chief of Staff"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.35,0:17:56.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I just had my hair cut.\NWhat do you think of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.63,0:17:58.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Don't come near me! Stop it!\N– Come on. Take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.30,0:18:02.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It looked like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.29,0:18:07.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What was?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.29,0:18:09.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What? The family meeting\Nyou had, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:14.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So, what? Are you playing hooky from\Nschool and going on a picnic tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.71,0:18:16.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A picnic?! That sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.30,0:18:19.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Say, Rukia…\N– Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.30,0:18:20.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,About my job as Soul Reaper…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.67,0:18:25.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Can I take the day off tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:28.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?\NWhat are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.88,0:18:33.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, you can't!\NWhat's going on with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:35.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You've been acting strange\Nsince this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:36.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's the day she died…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:40.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow's the anniversary\Nof the day my mom died.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.63,0:18:44.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's not quite right…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.21,0:18:46.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To be precise,\Nit's not the day she died…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:51.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,it's the day she was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.34,0:19:12.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Good morning, Inoue!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.55,0:19:15.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, he's going to skip school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.29,0:19:24.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If… If I were the rain…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.63,0:19:29.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,would I be able to connect with\Nsomeone's heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.29,0:19:36.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the way the rain connects\Nthe never-intersecting sky and earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.59,0:19:50.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.46,0:20:12.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.51,0:20:30.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Yay! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:31.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.65,0:20:35.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shucks…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.05,0:20:36.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:38.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.71,0:20:40.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.59,0:20:47.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.21,0:20:49.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, something just came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.88,0:20:51.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Aww no…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.80,0:20:52.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.55,0:20:54.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.30,0:21:00.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So, who is it today?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.17,0:21:04.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The thirteenth division's\NRukia Kuchiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.50,0:21:06.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kuchiki…?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.09,0:21:10.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And what has that\Nyoung lady done?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.17,0:21:14.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She has stayed too long\Nin the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.80,0:21:16.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.88,0:21:20.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We wouldn't call you out if that were all…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:23.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's something behind it.\NFind out what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.55,0:21:27.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can be a little rough, I take it?
